<chapter id="pvfs">
  <title>Setting up PVFS</title>

  <para>
    This chapter describes how to install and configure the <ulink
      url="http://parlweb.parl.clemson.edu/pvfs/index.html">Parallel Virtual
      File System</ulink> in a way that the fast communication capabilities
    provided by &ps; are used efficiently. This is neither an introduction to
    PVFS nor to parallel filesystems in general. In order to learn more about
    PVFS refer to the <ulink
      url="http://parlweb.parl.clemson.edu/pvfs/quick.html">Quick Start Guide
      to the Parallel Virtual File System</ulink>.
  </para>
